public class TriggerKeeper
extends java.lang.Object
implements Updateable, java.io.Serializable

This class is used to keep triggers. All events of inserted triggers are delayed until update() method is called

insertTrigger

public Trigger insertTrigger(Trigger t)
Insert instantiated trigger t. If t is instance of EvalTreeTrigger, DAG is used. Otherwise DelayedTrigger wrapping t is created and stored.

Parameters:
t - When you pass t into this function you can not use it. Use returned trigger instead of it
Returns:
Reference to the new trigger wrapping old one
